{"tid":820687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★澳門晚上9時發紅色風暴潮警戒訊號並鳴鐘提醒民眾撤離","createTime":"2018-09-15T14:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T14:32:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"70f1e17e383c9a16bbef7cf4286eeac020904c13","tid":820687,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"2018-09-15 HKT 22:21<br />\n <br />\n澳門在晚上9時首次用低鳴響鐘3分鐘然後廣播，提醒低窪地區居民，已經發出紅色風暴潮警戒訊號，需盡早撤離危險地方。澳門16個避險中心亦已經開放。<br />\n<br />\n其中一個低窪區臨時集合點的沙梨頭廣播站，鳴警期間未見有居民疏散，只有警員在路口戒備，維持交通。<br />\n<br />\n另外，受山竹影響，當局宣布連接珠海，原本24小時通關的三個口岸，在凌晨1時就會關閉。而來往港澳的客輪服務，在晚上10時開出尾班船之後停航。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1418051-20180915.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1418051-20180915.htm&d=S0akONC3rN1kuGo3BMaDKhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=c73fa3d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1418051-20180915.htm&h=8d4d059a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1418051-20180915.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bc81c27e95d4d54dc632c43c79e1bea8f1ddd215","tid":820687,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39596dab14cd17a94c1761d17f357717d2af5d18","tid":820687,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.168kk.com/uploads/allimg/171014/18-1G014121329.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.168kk.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F171014%2F18-1G014121329.jpg&h=ad995727&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5c224abffc359a3d77ab43f1234a7d4ef927796","tid":820687,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"d聲好似比人空襲咁"},{"pid":"18bceee21e92f7912eca1bdcbf11def898278939","tid":820687,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5c